---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hummingbird Social Studio | Editable Wedding Invitation Templates"
  description="Shop editable wedding invitation templates, bridal shower invitations, printable wedding stationery, and modern downloadable invitation suites from Hummingbird Social Studio."
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Editable wedding templates</p>
        <h1>Modern wedding stationery made simple.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Hummingbird Social Studio creates downloadable wedding invitation
          templates, bridal shower invitations, day-of stationery, and printable
          celebration designs with a soft, romantic, and modern feel.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/">
            Browse Wedding Invitations
          </a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/how-it-works/">
            See How It Works
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Shop by category</p>
        <h2>Wedding templates for every little detail.</h2>

        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/">
            <h3>Wedding Invitation Suites</h3>
            <p>
              Editable invitation templates with matching RSVP cards, detail
              cards, and coordinated stationery for modern weddings.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/bridal-shower-invitations/">
            <h3>Bridal Shower Invitations</h3>
            <p>
              Pretty, easy-to-edit bridal shower invite templates for brunches,
              garden parties, intimate gatherings, and stylish celebrations.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/custom-design-requests/">
            <h3>Custom Design Requests</h3>
            <p>
              Need a matching sign, menu, thank you card, or custom layout?
              Request a coordinated design in the Hummingbird Social Studio
              style.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-band">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why digital templates?</p>
        <h2>Download, edit, print, and celebrate.</h2>
        <p>
          Digital templates give you the flexibility to create beautiful wedding
          stationery without waiting on a fully custom design process. Choose a
          design you love, personalize the wording, update your event details,
          and print when you are ready.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every template is designed to feel polished and intentional, while
          still being simple enough for real-life wedding planning.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/how-it-works/">How It Works</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/printing-guide/">
            Read the Printing Guide
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Helpful planning guides</p>
        <h2>Everything you need to feel confident before you print.</h2>

        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/how-it-works/">
            <h3>How It Works</h3>
            <p>
              Learn how editable templates work, what happens after purchase,
              how to customize your design, and how to download your files.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/printing-guide/">
            <h3>Wedding Printing Guide</h3>
            <p>
              Find simple guidance on cardstock, paper finishes, envelope
              sizes, online printers, local print shops, and home printing.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/wording-etiquette/">
            <h3>Wording & Etiquette</h3>
            <p>
              Copy-and-paste wording ideas for adult-only weddings, cash bars,
              micro-weddings, elopements, family situations, and more.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our style</p>
        <h2>Soft romance, clean typography, and thoughtful details.</h2>
        <p>
          Hummingbird Social Studio is designed for couples and hosts who want
          stationery that feels elevated but approachable. The style blends warm
          neutrals, romantic details, vintage-inspired touches, modern layouts,
          and polished typography.
        </p>
        <p>
          From the first invitation to the final thank you card, each piece is
          created to help your event feel cohesive, beautiful, and easy to pull
          together.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/about/">About the Studio</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/faq/">Read the FAQ</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-band">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Popular template needs</p>
        <h2>Start with the piece you need most.</h2>

        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/">
            <h3>Wedding invitations</h3>
            <p>
              Editable invitation suites for formal weddings, intimate
              celebrations, destination weddings, and modern events.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/bridal-shower-invitations/">
            <h3>Bridal shower invites</h3>
            <p>
              Printable shower invitations for garden parties, brunch showers,
              modern bridal celebrations, and hosted gatherings.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/custom-design-requests/">
            <h3>Matching stationery</h3>
            <p>
              Request matching menus, signs, place cards, thank you cards, or
              coordinated day-of pieces for your celebration.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Questions before you order?</p>
        <h2>Planning should feel easier, not more confusing.</h2>
        <p>
          Not sure how editable templates work, what paper to choose, or whether
          a design can be adjusted for your event? Start with the support pages
          or reach out with your question.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/faq/">View Common Questions</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Contact the Studio</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
